1. End of Sentence Detection
own the data already have label: the sign: '.' whether ends the sentence

feature engineering:
each training data sample is a sentence, and extracting the previous and after 3 words surronding context of this sentence
extracting the number of the words  between '.' and the reliable sentence delimiter both right and left(previous and after)
extracting the number of spaces 

goal: need to predict whether '.' is the sentence delimiter(end of sentence: EOS(label))

auxiliary: build up the wordlists of abbreviation, title, special nouns and terms, since '.' is used in the delimiter of these words.

model:
decisiontree
lasso
